# Retrieval summary — outputs (real-data pilot)

- preset/model: M=42 dt=120.0s model_days=20.0 (n_steps≈14400), use_x64=True, emission=planck
- data: n_times=320, observed flux span=7058 ppm, obs_sigma=78 ppm, amplitude/noise=90.3
- SMC: kernel=mala, N=64, tempering_steps=37, final_beta=1.0000, final_ESS=61.7/64, mean_accept=0.64

